The article discusses the Tax Cuts and Jobs Act signed into law by President Donald J. Trump, which promises to result in more jobs, higher wages, and relief for middle-class families. It states that hardworking taxpayers will see more money in their paychecks as a result of the tax cuts. The article also mentions that the tax cuts will free up more money for families to provide for their needs and invest in their future. It highlights that President Trump has heard directly from taxpayers about how the tax cuts are improving their lives.